"{\"uid\": \"perezhilton.com-tom-cruise-olympics-closing-ceremony-stunt-pay\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"For any fan of action movies, the highlight of the closing ceremony of theParis 2024 Olympicshad to beTom Cruise.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 113, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheMission: Impossiblestar pulled a stunt in which he descended on a rope down from the ceiling of the Stade du France to the floor.\", \"from\": 115, \"to\": 247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 227, \"end\": 233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.993878114493074, \"rank\": 0.0020704975571880792, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He then took the Olympic rings flag on a motorcycle to a plane and flew it all the way to Los Angeles, the host city of 2028.\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 338, \"end\": 349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999991484979988, \"rank\": 8.502515471377664e-07, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He then parachuted down to the Hollywood sign and passed off the flag to local athletes.\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 462, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 405, \"end\": 419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"IT'S A BIRD.\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 471, \"end\": 475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bird_Internet_routing_daemon\", \"score\": 0.9999667835964603, \"rank\": 2.7219890923931998e-05, \"text\": \"BIRD\