]}, {\"sentence\": \"Apparently Cruise was just so fired up about the project and the Olympic games, he donated his time and energy (and risk of bodily harm!)\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"for no pay!\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Related: Tom Still Paying For Suri's EXPENSIVE College Tuition Despite Estrangement!\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1226, \"end\": 1230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duniya_Suri\", \"score\": 0.6465393040611809, \"rank\": 0.44171273870256683, \"text\": \"Suri\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duniya_Suri\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duniya_Suri\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LA28presidentCasey Wassermantold the story during aCNBC x Boardroom: Game Planpanel in Santa Monica this week.\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1392, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1369, \"end\": 1381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Monica_Boulevard\", \"score\": 0.998816320718463, \"rank\": 0.0011850820385827607, \"text\": \"Santa Monica\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Monica_Boulevard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Monica_Boulevard\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He recalled:  \\\"The best part of the story is we pitched on a Zoom, and the original idea was a person in the stadium as a stunt double.\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are like, 'Well, there is no way we are getting this.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1585, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are going to get four hours of filming time.\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We will do the thing that the L.A. with the Hollywood sign, he will hand the thing off and he's done.\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1735, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1664, \"end\": 1668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999970465692471, \"rank\": 2.953439383116291e-06, \"text\": \"L.A.\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 1678, \"end\": 1692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe we will get the other stuff and the rest will be just a stunt double.'\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1812, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"About five minutes into the presentation [Tom Cruise] goes, 'I am in.\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1855, \"end\": 1865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am only doing it if I get to do everything.'\\\"\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1934, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And he did!\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 1947, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wasserman detailed:  \\\"He finished filming Mission: Impossible at 6 p.m. in London, got right on a plane.\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 2052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1948, \"end\": 1957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\", \"score\": 0.9968261504346664, \"rank\": 0.0031534505964983402, \"text\": \"Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lew_Wasserman\"}, {\"begin\": 2023, \"end\": 2029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999960263223